		<title>Interaction Nets 论文集</title>
		<published>2022-03-08T17:36:12+00:00</published>
		<updated>2022-03-08T17:36:12+00:00</updated>
		<link href="https://wtzlas.github.io/posts/interaction-nets-papers/" type="text/html"/>
		<id>https://wtzlas.github.io/posts/interaction-nets-papers/</id>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt;一些Interaction nets和用其实现Lambda reduction方向上的论文&#x2F;文章列表。&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;纯Interaction nets方向：&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;link.springer.com&#x2F;chapter&#x2F;10.1007&#x2F;10704567_10&quot;&gt;A Calculus for Interaction Nets&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maribel Fernández, Ian Mackie (1999)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.sciencedirect.com&#x2F;science&#x2F;article&#x2F;pii&#x2F;S1571066105803639&quot;&gt;Interaction Nets with McCarthy&#x27;s amb&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Maribel Fernández, Lionel Khalil (2002)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.sciencedirect.com&#x2F;science&#x2F;article&#x2F;pii&#x2F;S1571066105826143&quot;&gt;Weak Reduction and Garbage Collection in Interaction Net&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jorge Sousa Pinto (2003)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;arxiv.org&#x2F;abs&#x2F;1702.06092&quot;&gt;Parallel needed reduction for pure interaction nets&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anton Salikhmetov (2017)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;arxiv.org&#x2F;abs&#x2F;1505.07164&quot;&gt;An Implementation Model for Interaction Nets&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Abubakar Hassan, Ian Mackie, Shinya Sato (2015)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;sro.sussex.ac.uk&#x2F;id&#x2F;eprint&#x2F;54469&#x2F;&quot;&gt;Design and implementation of a low-level language for interaction nets&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shinya Sato (2015)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interaction nets与Lambda reduction结合方向：&lt;&#x2F;strong&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.phil.uu.nl&#x2F;%7Eoostrom&#x2F;publication&#x2F;pdf&#x2F;lambdascope.pdf&quot;&gt;Lambdascope: Another optimal implementation of the lambda-calculus&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Vincent van Oostrom, Kees-Jan van de Looij, Marijn Zwitserlood (2004)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;link.springer.com&#x2F;chapter&#x2F;10.1007&#x2F;978-3-642-24452-0_3&quot;&gt;An Interaction Net Implementation of Closed Reduction&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ian Mackie (2008)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;arxiv.org&#x2F;abs&#x2F;1304.2290&quot;&gt;Macro Lambda Calculus&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anton Salikhmetov (2013)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https:&#x2F;&#x2F;arxiv.org&#x2F;abs&#x2F;1710.07516&quot;&gt;An impure solution to the problem of matching fans&lt;&#x2F;a&gt;&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Anton Salikhmetov (2017)&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
&lt;&#x2F;blockquote&gt;
</content>
